From Paul Havemann Subject Re Clinton's immunization program In article mwilson Mark Wilson writes On the news last night Clinton was bashing the republicans for stonewalling his so called stimulus It seems that one small item within this package was going to pay for free immunizations for poor So now Clinton is claiming that the republicans are holding the health of poor kids hostage for blatantly political Aside from the merits or lack thereof of another free immunization program just what is such a program doing in a bill that is supposedly about creating Jobs What the hell have jobs to do with it It's another touchy feely program from the new vapid The fact is the major claim made for universal immunization that all children will be immunized has absolutely no Several states already have programs have had these programs for years The result on average their success rates are no better than the national It seems that the gummint hasn't yet figured out a way to MAKE parents bring their kids Yet another case of shameless demagoguery from the new Democrats the agents of If Clinton is so hot to get this immunization program why doesn't he and the democrats just introduce it as a stand alone Isn't it possible that Clinton is the one doing the blatant political read pork manipulations He is telling the republicans pass my muti billion dollar package or I will go to the people and tell them that you are opposed to immunizing poor What Clinton using this issue for partisan gain Do I have never thought highly of Clinton but stunts like this lower my opinion of him even I thought one of Clinton's campaign themes was that he was going to be a new kind of This kind of manuevering would have made LBJ All together c'mon you know the Meet the new boss Same as the old boss And the chorus We won't get fooled again Paul Havemann Internet They're not just opinions they're caffeine for the brain Up to milligrams per cynical Recommended Minimum Daily Requirement Keep